events.text: Tok, tok, tok. Thumb, thumb, thumb.
Some triangles appear to be jumping into the ceiling to get stuck.
Yooo! You can see the whole party from up here!!
Let’s go! My turn!
The triangle jumps up into the ceiling
Wooohoooo, Awesome! Glorious! What a jump!
Wooow good job Spike! You’re so awesome!
Yah you are the best Spike!
No you two are the best! You stuck way better to the ceiling then I did!
All the triangles are pointing towards each other will giving compliments, a lot of compliments.
Hey Hexagon shape! Out of the way!
Right after hearing that, a triangle falls on top of you. Auch.
[i]Ouch, how did I not notice them? Am I hexed?[/i]
Hi pal, are you ok? I’m so sorry for falling onto you!
Auch, that’s... I’m ok…
Really really sorry, hopefully I didn’t hurt you. You have some amazing looking points. I bet those would be great for sticking to ceilings.
Yah you look great! You have twice as many points as we do!
Yah such a cool shape you are! So exotic!
What do you think, want to join our little jumping game? The view is amazing up top
Well, unfortunately my forehead is flat so I dont think I can stick to the ceiling...
One of the triangles hands you a triangle shaped hat.
Here, have this hat, it should help you!!
